                      <h1>Hey, I'm Khadija üëã</h1>
                      <p>I'm a second year design student studying at York University. My interests lie mainly within digital product   and interaction design, however I'm very keen to explore further within the discipline. What fascinates me about design is taking part in building the relationship that humans have developed with their day to day digital products. Creating a seamless experience that feels natural to the use is what I aim to achieve in my work. I enjoy analyzing user behaviour to determine a viable solution to all things around us. 
                        <br> <br>
                      Some things I hope to explore include 3d modelling, motion and packaging design. On the side, I have a passion for photography and am looking to build on my interests in film and videography. 
                        <br> <br>
                      I'm currently open to summer internship/freelance opportunities in digital product design, UI/UX, or similar.
                      </p>
